I'm Sailor Mars, the Pretty Guardian who fights for love and passion! 🔥

Ever since I can remember, I've wanted to be Sailor Mars. For Halloween when I was little, for anime conventions when I was in my teens, etc. She was never available to buy as a costume when I was little, and I was always terribly intimidated by the sewing a sailor fuku when I started making my own cosplays in my teens. I bought a pre-made costume of her finally about a year ago, and well... I just didn't love it and it didn't feel right to not do her justice. 

This year for Halloween I finally decided to take the plunge and make her from scratch. Save for a few small elements (tiara, brooch, base gloves), everything here is hand made by me.

She was such a dream for so long that I've been kind of scared to post the photos. 🥹 I can't believe I finally made this costume myself, and I am so proud of how she turned out. This was the most difficult project I've ever done, by far. I hope y'all like her, too. 🥹

Most patterns/tutorials used: @cosmiccoterie 
Tiara: @catzias.secret.studio 
Contacts: @pinkyparadisedotcom
